narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned what Public Humanities is, which I had previously not known that it existed. I learned how to interact with the community while understanding my place and amplifying the voices of others.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! This Professor is amazing and Yale students need to explore what lies beyond the Yale bubble. I loved this class so much!
